            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 14 of the SLEEP program. The script targets the mental loop: the mind that chases the same thought circuit in the belief that one more pass will resolve it. A daytime practice for stepping out of the spin."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though my mind loops the same worries on repeat, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I chase thoughts to feel in control, I honour that it just leaves me depleted." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I'm tired of the loop, I'm open to stepping out of it today." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " The loop promises certainty but delivers fatigue." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I rehearse conversations and plan problems that don't exist." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm trying to think my way to safety." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " It keeps me stuck in the spin." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I can recognise the loop and choose not to follow." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I can interrupt it with breath, with tapping, with presence." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm allowed to let a thought pass unanswered." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I reclaim my attention from the loop." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I choose clarity over compulsion." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I don't need to finish every thought." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I can let them drift by like clouds." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " My nervous system steadies as I stop chasing." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Stillness brings the wisdom I was trying to think into existence." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I am safe without mental overwork." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " My mind rests in quiet focus." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Peace replaces the loop today." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times." }]
      },
